    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html>

    <head>
        <style>
            body {
                background-image: url('images/tarot-front.jpg');
                background-size: cover;
                background-position: center;
                transition: background-image 3s ease-in-out;
            }

            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                background: url('images/tarot-front.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
                background-size: cover;
                position: fixed;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                font-family: 'matura-mt-script-capitals-regular', sans-serif;
            }

            .content-box {
                text-align: center;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 20px;
                background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                left: 50%;
                transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
                max-width: 1000px;
                max-height: 500px;
                border-radius: 15px;
            }


            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                color: burlywood;
                font-size: 38px;
                margin: 0;
            }

            p {
                color: goldenrod;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.7;
                margin: 0;
                font-family: 'matura-mt-script-capitals-regular', sans-serif;
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Tarot Reading Page</h1>
                <br>
                <p>
                    Welcome to the mystical world of tarot readings! Tarot cards have been used for centuries as a tool
                    for gaining insight into the past, present, and future. Each card in the deck carries a unique
                    symbolism and meaning, offering a glimpse into the energies surrounding your life.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Many people turn to tarot during moments of introspection, decision-making, or when faced with
                    life's twists and turns. Take a moment, shuffle the cards, and embark on a journey of self-discovery
                    through the ancient art of tarot.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            const images = ['images/tarot-front.jpg', 'images/card1.jpg', 'images/card2.jpg', 'images/card3.jpg'];
            let currentIndex = 0;

            function changeBackground() {
                currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % images.length;
                document.body.style.backgroundImage = `url('${images[currentIndex]}')`;
            }

            setInterval(changeBackground, 4000);
        </script>
    </body>
    </html>
</div>
